Package: boosterpak
Title: Reusable Project Capability Packs
Version: 0.6.3
Authors@R: 
    person("Sean", "Thimons", email = "sxthimons@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Sean Thimons [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Sean Thimons <sxthimons@gmail.com>
Description: Provides reusable project packs for bootstrapping R workflows. A
    pack is a typed bundle of package dependencies, optional source
    specifications, startup attachment intent, helper-function sidecars, and
    project-local setup conventions. Applies packs with 'pak' and 'renv' while
    leaving exact version restoration to 'renv' lockfiles.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://seanthimons.github.io/boosterpak/, https://github.com/seanthimons/boosterpak
BugReports: https://github.com/seanthimons/boosterpak/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
